OL,3,CMum who killed young sons in school-
OL,4,Crun crash spared jail
OL,6,FA mother who killed her two young sons
OL,7,Fin a crash caused by a defective tyre
OL,8,Fon their way home from school has been
OL,9,Fspared jail.
OL,11,FAmy Sheppard's eight-year-old son
OL,12,FLouie Ellis and his brother Mason,
OL,13,Faged six, were in her Vauxhall Astra
OL,14,Fwhen she crashed with an Audi car on
OL,15,Fthe A52 between Sandilands and
OL,16,FHuttoft, near Sutton on Sea,
OL,17,FLincolnshire.
OL,19,FEllis died at the scene, Mason died in
OL,20,Fhospital. Their four-year-old brother
OL,21,Fwas also injured but survived.
