OL,3,CMum who killed young sons in school-
OL,4,Crun crash spared jail
OL,6,FTwo people in an Audi were also
OL,7,Finjured in the incident on 2 October
OL,8,F2023.
OL,10,FSheppard, who had already admitted
OL,11,Fcausing death and serious injury by
OL,12,Fcareless driving, was given a 20-month
OL,13,Fsuspended prison sentence and was
OL,14,Fbanned from driving for two years.
OL,16,FJudge James House KC told Lincoln
OL,17,FCrown Court the sentence was "an act
OL,18,Fof mercy".
OL,20,F"Her carelessness caused the death of
OL,21,Fher two sons," he said.
