OL,6,F"It has long been recognised there are
OL,7,Fexceptional cases which come before
OL,8,Fthe courts."
OL,10,FLincoln Crown Court heard Sheppard, of
OL,11,FMumby Road, Hutoft, had picked her two
OL,12,Fsons up from primary school in
OL,13,FMablethorpe after finishing her job as
OL,14,Fa nursery nurse when the crash
OL,15,Fhappened.
OL,17,FExaminations after the crash showed a
OL,18,Frear tyre had a pressure reading of
OL,19,Fjust five psi, although the court
OL,20,Fheard it could have lost pressure
OL,21,Fduring the crash.
