OL,4,Crun crash spared jail
OL,6,FDavid Eager, prosecuting, said
OL,7,FSheppard had sent her partner a
OL,8,FWhatsApp message the previous day
OL,9,Fwhich said: "My tyre is going flat
OL,10,Fagain."
OL,12,FThe man had checked the wrong tyre,
OL,13,Fwhich gave a reading of 32 psi.
OL,15,F"Sadly, tragically, he did not check
OL,16,Fany of the other tyres," Mr Eager
OL,17,Fadded.
OL,19,FThe court heard another driver noticed
OL,20,Fthe under-inflated tyre as he
OL,21,Ftravelled behind Sheppard's car.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
