OL,6,FMr Eager said the driver was so
OL,7,Fconcerned that he dropped backwards
OL,8,Fand noticed the Astra was "wallowing."
OL,10,F"The back end went, it turned 45
OL,11,Fdegrees," the driver said.
OL,13,F"It must have been like it appeared
OL,14,Ffrom nowhere to the guy in the Audi."
OL,16,FIn a statement Mason and Louie's
OL,17,Ffather, Laurie Ellis, who was
OL,18,Fseparated from Sheppard, described
OL,19,FMason as "always cheeky, always
OL,20,Fsmiling."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
