OL,6,F"Losing him feels like losing part of
OL,7,Fmyself," he said
OL,9,FHe said Louie loved watching football
OL,10,Fwith him.
OL,12,F"I miss the little things the most,"
OL,13,FMr Ellis added.
OL,15,FMr Ellis said his pain had also been
OL,16,Fmade worse by Sheppard's behaviour
OL,17,Ftowards him both before, and after the
OL,18,Fcollision.
